=======================================================
Program (C Code)
=======================================================
void main() {
    int T1 = 1, T2 = 1;

    while(1) {
        T2 = T1 + 1;
        T1 = T2;
    }
}


=======================================================
Explanation
=======================================================
Here T1 and T2 must be equivalent after the second 
statement inside the while loop.
